title: SC EP:9 A look back at 2013 in the Bigfoot world
itunes:title: SC EP:9 A look back at 2013 in the Bigfoot world
description: In this episode we take a look back at the some of the things that have happened in the bigfoot world in 2013. Join us as we will be discussing Bigfoot encounters and Bigfoot stories. Wes, Woody and Will will also be discussing Sasquatch behavior and encounters. As always we will be playing some of our favorite Sasquatch encounters.
